snippet.title: Record Tripping
snippet.description: Record Tripping Use your mouse's scroll wheel to scratch your way through all five chapters of this puzzle game.

snippet.title: Recordshop Tycoon
snippet.description: Recordshop Tycoon Earn cash selling records. Become the most wealthy record shop tycoon of the Rubato Hills.

snippet.title: Wrath
snippet.description: Wrath Bestow the wrath of God on the pitiful creatures of the Earth.

snippet.title: String Avoider
snippet.description: String Avoider Avoid the walls and guide your string through all 26 levels. Hit the scissor to cut the string in half.

snippet.title: Death Walker
snippet.description: Death Walker Become the greatest tight-rope walker ever by walking a specially constructed razor sharp rope.

snippet.title: Hanging Around
snippet.description: Hanging Around Use your rope to ceiling from ceiling to ceiling. Try to get as far as possible, but don't fall on the floor.

snippet.title: Jump In
snippet.description: Jump In Show your jump rope skills! Pass a level in 3 tries to unlock new clothes and backgrounds.

snippet.title: Ninja+
snippet.description: Ninja+ Use a combination of Ninja Rope skill and Kunai throwing to collect all of the coins as fast as possible.

snippet.title: Gibbets
snippet.description: Gibbets Use your bow and arrows to shoot the ropes and release the prisoners. Watch out, don't kill them!

snippet.title: Ninja Ball
snippet.description: Ninja Ball Swing on your rope and collect the stars before you run out of time to advance to the next level.
